WEBVTT

00:01.521 --> 00:05.023
===MUTANT X Under The Cloak Of War / s02.ep15===

00:04.504 --> 00:06.506
MAN, I HATE THESE THINGS.

00:06.506 --> 00:09.107
A BUNCH OF RICH PEOPLE STANDING
AROUND CONGRATULATING EACH

00:09.108 --> 00:11.010
OTHER ON HOW MUCH BETTER
THEY ARE THAN EVERYONE ELSE.

00:11.010 --> 00:14.412
WELL, IT'S GOOD TO
SEE THE TAILOR LEFT ROOM FOR
THE CHIP ON YOUR SHOULDER.

00:14.412 --> 00:16.215
MAN, YOU DON'T LIKE THESE
THINGS ANY MORE THAN I DO.

00:16.215 --> 00:19.818
NO, I DON'T. BUT
IT'S WHERE I CAME FROM.

00:19.818 --> 00:21.820
THE TRICK, YOU SEE,
IS THAT NOBODY DOES.

00:22.221 --> 00:24.623
YOU JUST GOT TO BE COOL
ENOUGH NOT TO LET IT SHOW.

00:24.623 --> 00:25.225
YEAH, WHATEVER.

00:27.625 --> 00:30.629
WELL, AT LEAST ADAM
SEEMS TO BE ENJOYING HIMSELF.

00:30.629 --> 00:33.233
WELL, IT'S GOOD TO SEE HIM OUT.

00:36.233 --> 00:38.237
OH. WOW.

00:38.637 --> 00:39.639
YOU GUYS LOOK AMAZING.

00:39.639 --> 00:42.842
YEAH, BUT I
DON'T KNOW HOW I'M GOING TO
CLIMB A WALL IN THIS THING.

00:43.243 --> 00:44.844
SO...?

00:49.249 --> 00:50.050
AREN'T YOU GOING
TO SAY ANYTHING?

00:50.050 --> 00:52.452
YOU LOOK GOOD.

00:52.452 --> 00:56.856
YOU LOOK REALLY GOOD.

00:56.856 --> 01:01.261
REGULATION OF
ADVANCED GENETIC FUNDING IS
IN EVERYBODY'S INTERESTS.

01:01.661 --> 01:05.265
FINALLY, SOMEONE
WHO TELLS THE TRUTH.

01:05.665 --> 01:08.468
ALL THE OTHERS ARE WORRIED
ABOUT IS THEIR PRECIOUS FUNDING.

01:08.468 --> 01:10.870
I'D LIKE TO THINK SO.
THANK YOU.

01:11.271 --> 01:12.472
I'M SORRY, I DON'T KNOW YOU.

01:12.472 --> 01:13.673
I'M ADAM KANE.

01:14.074 --> 01:15.275
SERENA.

01:15.275 --> 01:16.476
SERENA...?

01:16.876 --> 01:18.878
JUST SERENA.

01:18.878 --> 01:21.281
I'M SORRY, SO, ARE
YOU INTERESTED IN GENETICS?

01:21.281 --> 01:24.084
I WORK IN THE GENE
SEQUENCING LAB AT BERKELEY.

01:24.084 --> 01:25.285
REALLY?

01:25.285 --> 01:28.488
YOU DON'T SEEM LIKE
YOUR AVERAGE SCIENTIST.

01:28.488 --> 01:30.490
WELL, NOW YOU'RE
BEING JUDGMENTAL.

01:30.490 --> 01:32.892
I'D EXPECTED MORE FROM YOU.

01:32.892 --> 01:35.295
WELL, I'M SORRY
TO DISAPPOINT YOU.

01:35.295 --> 01:38.098
I'LL HAVE TO FIND A WAY
FOR YOU TO MAKE IT UP TO ME.

01:38.098 --> 01:41.701
MAYBE I COULD BUY YOU A DRINK.

01:43.703 --> 01:48.108
WELL... THERE'S ANOTHER
SIDE OF ADAM WE'RE SEEING.

01:48.108 --> 01:50.110
HOW MUCH DO YOU WANT TO
BET HE TAKES HER HOME TONIGHT?

01:50.110 --> 01:50.910
NO WAY.

01:51.311 --> 01:52.512
AW, COME ON, ADAM'S A MAN.

01:52.512 --> 01:55.315
AND SHE IS...
DEFINITELY A WOMAN.

01:55.315 --> 02:01.321
DOUBLE OR NOTHING THEY
SHARE BREAKFAST IN THE MORNING.

02:03.723 --> 02:05.325
SO TELL ME ABOUT YOURSELF.

02:05.725 --> 02:06.926
MYSELF...

02:06.926 --> 02:08.928
I TOLD YOU WHERE I WORK.

02:08.928 --> 02:10.530
I KNOW, BUT, YOU KNOW,
SOMETHING MORE PERSONAL,

02:10.930 --> 02:12.132
LIKE YOUR LAST NAME.

02:12.132 --> 02:13.333
SERENA WHAT?

02:13.733 --> 02:15.335
AHH, MY LAST NAME.

02:15.335 --> 02:17.737
WELL, IT'S A SECRET.

02:17.737 --> 02:19.739
REALLY? WELL, I'M
GOOD AT KEEPING SECRETS.

02:19.739 --> 02:21.341
REALLY?
YEAH.

02:21.341 --> 02:25.745
ALL RIGHT, THEN.

02:28.148 --> 02:29.349
REALLY?

02:29.349 --> 02:30.550
UH HUH.

02:30.550 --> 02:31.751
WELL, THAT'S A BEAUTIFUL NAME.

02:31.751 --> 02:32.952
NOW, THERE'S ONLY ONE THING.

02:33.353 --> 02:34.154
UH HUH?

02:34.154 --> 02:35.355
NOW THAT YOU KNOW...

02:35.355 --> 02:36.556
UH HUH.

02:36.956 --> 02:38.958
I'M GOING TO HAVE TO KILL YOU.

